name: Voyager I
description: Space prove Voyager I carries a gold-plated audio-visual disc that is intended for any intelligent extraterrestrial life form who may find it. Cover of the disc has instructional diagrams for playing the record and extracting the images. The recording includes greeting in 55 languages, samples of music around the world, sounds of Earth, images of cultural and natural life on Earth and diagrams of our scientific discoveries. Voyager I is currently the farthest human-made object from Earth.
